Install Flatpak  (https://flatpak.org/setup/Ubuntu/)

1) To install Flatpak on Ubuntu 18.10 (Cosmic Cuttlefish) or Ubuntu 19.04 (Disco Dingo), simply run:
      sudo apt install flatpak
  
2) Install the Software Flatpak plugin
      sudo apt install gnome-software-plugin-flatpak
      
3) Add the Flathub repository
    flatpak remote-add --if-not-exists flathub https://flathub.org/repo/flathub.flatpakrepo
    
4) To complete setup, restart your system.
    
